 &lt;td style="text-align: left">1960 - 2153&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table></description></item><item><title>Samurai Leveling Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/leveling-guide/</link><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 06:49:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/leveling-guide/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="level-50">Level 50&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://ffxivrotations.com/3et8">Level 50 Opener&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Rotate through your combos and smash that Midare button. Use Meikyo for Gekko and Kasha past the opener. Refresh Higanbana as close to 0 as possible.&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="level-52">Level 52&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Introduces Kenki Gauge and Hissatsu: Shinten. Use it when you want and be sure not to overcap.&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="level-60">Level 60&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://ffxivrotations.com/3lvo">Level 60 Opener&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Once you begin accruing Kenki to spend on Shinten, the opener should look like this.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Samurai FAQ</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/faq/</link><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 06:27:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/faq/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Is X better than Y for me?&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>For weapons: item level (ilvl)/weapon damage (wd) wins, regardless of substats.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>For armor: ilvl usually wins, unless 5 materia slots.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>For same-ilvl pieces: substat itemization can be in your favor or not depending on the rest of your gear and stat tiering.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>When in doubt, use the Gear Planner - only here can you get an accurate answer for your setup!&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Samurai has positionals?!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Samurai Advanced Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/advanced-guide/</link><pubDate>Mon, 26 Sep 2022 03:15:49 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/advanced-guide/</guid><description>&lt;p>Oops, we don&amp;rsquo;t have that guide yet! Interested in contributing? Feel free to join the &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/thebalanceffxiv">Balance Discord server&lt;/a> to contact a job mentor/admin and express your interest!&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>